      <p>Our diversity of sporting and athletic success, I believe, is the best evidence for my argument. Additionally, we have a fervent culture of sport domestically – the AFL boasts one of the top 10 largest average crowds for a domestic league in the world, and comfortably the largest in the southern hemisphere.</p>

